Julian Weaver was principal of Davis Senior High School Davis High School from 1990 to 1993.  He began his career as a high school teacher at http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Victor_Valley_High_School Victor Valley High School in 1970 and worked his way up to principal of the high school in 1981, just prior to his moving to Davis High School.  After Davis he continued his school administrative career in San Bernadino County and the Victor Valley Union High School District before retiring in 2008.

